Package: ntpd
Submenu: Time Synchronization
Version: 4.2.8p6-1
Depends: +libc +USE_EGLIBC:librt +USE_EGLIBC:libpthread +libopenssl +libpthread +libcap
Menu-Depends: 
Provides: 
Section: net
Category: Network
Title: ISC ntp server
Maintainer: Peter Wagner <tripolar@gmx.at>
Source: ntp-4.2.8p6.tar.gz
Type: ipkg
Description:  The ISC ntp suite is a collection of tools used to synchronize the
 system clock with remote NTP time servers and run/monitor local NTP
 servers.
 .
 This package contains the ntpd server.
http://www.ntp.org/
Peter Wagner <tripolar@gmx.at>
@@

